203
00:07:17.654 --> 00:07:20.265
[forced laughing]

204
00:07:20.309 --> 00:07:21.876
No. we're good.
Thank you.

205
00:07:21.919 --> 00:07:23.791
Yeah. uh. my friend thinks that
you're her favourite writer

206
00:07:23.834 --> 00:07:25.270
