let's get you settled in.

262
00:09:20.472 --> 00:09:20.995
Okay.

263
00:09:21.038 --> 00:09:22.170
- May I?
- Sure.

264
00:09:22.213 --> 00:09:22.823
Thank you.

265
00:09:22.866 --> 00:09:23.911
